{"tid":332524,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[大台劇情節]如果俾你遇到咁既情況,你仲會繼續同女友一齊嗎?","createTime":"2017-07-23T05:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T12:08:40.000Z","uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db85995eaeee1a38cbc764e32146bf2536864aca","tid":332524,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"你以前讀書個陣鐘意過一個女仔<br />\n但因為種種原因,一直都冇同人表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來大家出來做野之後各有各生活,佢之後仲識咗男友結埋婚<br />\n佢男友係個D咩柒野金融才俊,都叫有錢,佢地結咗婚之後都係住偽豪宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然係咁,但你都依然祝福佢<br />\n佢結婚個陣都有請你去飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實比一比,人地起嗎都叫有D錢住偽豪宅,自己只係草根窮L,邊到配得上人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來過咗一排,你終於都出到pool<br />\n你同條女拍咗一段時間,佢想你同佢屋企人見面食下飯<br />\n你當然答應<br />\n到咗個日,佢叫咗佢屋企人出來,你先嚇一跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來個金融撚同你以前鐘意條女都係佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個一刻,你覺得世界好撚細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁既情況,你覺得之後應該點做?<br />\n覺得冇咩野繼續同女友一齊?<br />\n定係驚尷尬決定分開?<br />\n如果繼續一齊,你又接唔接受得到你以前鐘意既女會做你長輩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882844b9dca92832224f51086c9bfd852c972c27","tid":332524,"uid":21423,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:18:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53d3e22c82f6c6fc7387cd02c92a37dc2d48a292","tid":332524,"uid":9